```html
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Assistant Interface</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 20px;
        }
        #dialogue-box {
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
